---
title: Italian Meatloaves with Green Beans and Mashed Potatoes
description: Spiked with aromatic basil, these mini meatloaves are what happens when an American classic spends a semester abroad in Rome. Their piccolo size doesn’t just make them adorable; it allows them to cook quickly, too. Even the mashed potatoes on the side, fragrant with garlic, sneak in a little European flair.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6048c68393c2041aed37abd7-e3ade513.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/italian-meatloaf-6048c68393c2041aed37abd7-7285f255.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/italian-meatloaves-6048c68393c2041aed37abd7
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 640 kcal
  fat: 32 g
  saturated fat: 12 g
